                              </figcaption>
                      </figure>
        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-10-123711-150x150.png" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-10-123711.png" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-10-123711-980x551.png 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-10-123711-1440x810.png 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2023585">
          <figure style="height:560px;">
            <div class="image" style="background-image:url('https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Screenshot-2024-05-10-123711-980x551.png'); background-color:#000"></div>
                          <figcaption id="caption-2023585">
                <span class="icon caption-arrow icon-drop-indicator"></span>
                                  <div class="caption">
                    A lot of the characters in Cryptmaster are, well, characters.                  </div>
                                                  <div class="credit">
                    <span class="icon icon-camera"></span>
